          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*. Data tables of subent 14-28 give",
                "estimated cross sections for the (p,xn+p) and (p,xn+2p)",
                "reactions. In this case target isotopes were not",
                "determined uniquely. More than one target isotope can",
                "contribute to yields of product nuclides. The target",
                "isotopes given in subent 1-13 have the smallest x and",
                "are likely to have the largest cross sections for the",
                "product nuclides of interest. Smaller values given for",
                "The cross sections correspond to the case in which all",
                "the possible target isotopes were assumed to have the",
                "same cross section and larger values to the case in",
                "which only the target isotopes with the smallest x",
                "were assumed to contribute to the yields."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CRITIQUE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Data presented in the data tables are doubtful,",
                "because it is not clear how authors succeeuded in",
                "separating of reaction channels. Very much reaction",
                "channels are opened for 12 GeV energy."
              ]
            }
          ],
